title: NoTrender Rain 8/10: 5th, Armie Hammer, Jennette McCurdy, Trump, Sean Bean, Netflix
itunes:title: NoTrender Rain 8/10: 5th, Armie Hammer, Jennette McCurdy, Trump, Sean Bean, Netflix
description:
In this edition of NoTrender Rain, Jack and Miles discuss Trump pleading the 5th, the new Armie Hammer doc, the Jennette McCurdy memoir, Trump supporters' reaction to the Mar-A-Lago raid, Sean Bean's thoughts on intimacy coordinators, and how people neither know nor care that Netflix has mobile games!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
